data.title: City Life International Church
data.meta_description: City Life is a vibrant spirit filled multi-cultural church affiliated with the Assemblies of God. We are situated at the heart of Kelham Island which is known for its heritage linked to steel industries. As an international church we have 7 core values, which help to shape us into the people we should be. By embodying […]
